### Start a new conversation (JSON)
POST http://localhost:7071/api/agents/HostedAgent/run
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "message": "Co wiesz o eventach w Lublinie?"
}

###

### Continue a conversation — replace <thread_id> with the ID returned above
POST http://localhost:7071/api/agents/HostedAgent/run
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "message": "O jakie miasto chodzi?",
    "thread_id": "a5457ed9-59cd-4bad-bbc1-5d2db11505c2"
}